Hi everyone,

Last minute golf at Cyprian Keyes in Boylston.

Its $59 for walking; $78 for riding.  $5 for a bucket of balls at the driving range.

I've reserved 8 spots for tomorrow (9:40am and 9:50am) but I'll have to call the course by the end of today to confirm the number.  If you're intersted, please rsvp as soon as possible so you don't get locked out.  Also, if you miss the deadline, call me directly 339-224-1377 and I'll see what I can do (assuming they'll have a hard time booking any spot I cancel overnight :)     Sorry for the last minute notice.....
